  warning [compiler-options-not-pinned] "compilerOptions.strict" is not set in deno.json. Deno currently type-checks deno.json projects with an implicit "strict": true, while stock TypeScript — which Deno 3's type checking is based on — defaults to false.
    fix: set "compilerOptions.strict": true (pins Deno's current implicit default)
  warning [compiler-options-not-pinned] "compilerOptions.noImplicitOverride" is not set in deno.json. Deno currently type-checks deno.json projects with an implicit "noImplicitOverride": true, while stock TypeScript — which Deno 3's type checking is based on — defaults to false.
    fix: set "compilerOptions.noImplicitOverride": true (pins Deno's current implicit default)

